AEW Dynamite opens with Daniel Garcia being interviewed by Renee Paquette about tonight's match against Will Ospreay for the International Championship.

He swears on his mothers life he will beat Ospreay.

MJF offers to be in Garcia's corner tonight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3102938e-cabf-4a91-95a7-19304425facd/20240703_170825.jpg)

*   ## **_OWEN HART CUP: BRYAN DANIELSON DEF. PAC_**
    

Excellent match. No notes.

