![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4b8338ee-fad9-4d7f-b97a-f99443a91525/20240703_172517.jpg)

## **_NOTHING MATTERS, SMILE ANYWAY!!!!!!!_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e64826e2-ac97-4058-929d-502ca61951dd/PhotoGrid_1_20240703173836.jpg)

Mark Briscoe is the first person in AEW to step up against the Elite in Blood and Guts.

Briscoe gets jumped by Jack Perry, Kyle O'Reilly runs in, then Okada runs in followed by the Bucks.

The Elite takes down their enemies and poses over them until the Acclaimed comes out to run them off

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/128cfbb3-98f8-4a85-a7cf-5335cac2b563/Screenshot_20240703-174506_TrillerTV.jpg)

*   ## **_WILLOW NIGHTINGALE DEF. KRIS STATLANDER TO ADVANCE TO THE FINALS OF THE OWEN CUP_**
    

Its a very aggressive match and at the end Stokely Hathaway tries to help Kris Statlander cheat and ends up costing her the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/14849912-e347-4b77-abcc-19506bed0a50/20240703_180012.jpg)

Britt Baker revealed that the entire right side of her body stopped working and she was diagnosed in Hospital with TIA (transient ischaemic attack)

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1c4200cf-39b4-4eab-a79b-9a14f678c02a/Messenger_creation_65184d44-07f8-4665-9d7d-649f5a9be427.jpeg)

"You are a CEO that we can actually get behind." - Nicholas Jackson to Mercedes Mone

HEEL MERCEDES HAS ARRIVED!!!!!!

The crew doesnt let Brit Baker finish talking as they start setting up Mercedes Mone Celebration while she's still standing in the ring.

Britt says Mercedes can't get the crowd to chant three letters without manipulating them with her theme music.

But Britt is D. M. D.

Mercedes arrives. Gets compliments from the EVPs and heads to the ring. Mercedes and Britt are face to face for the first time.

Britt wants her at All In. Mercedes puts her hand in Britts face and says back of the line.

Britt gets in Mercedes face and it seems we have some problems between these ladies now

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/baa28ccd-552f-4389-8d45-1d5cde4e43db/20240703_180229.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/70b0b8c4-6e14-4fda-a4b9-f56bb9159125/20240703_181659.jpg)

WILL OSPREAY IS OFFICIALLY OUT OF THE DON CALLIS FAMILY.

Ospreay requested he be allowed to leave because he's not built for the evil stuff the DCF does.

Don Callis says it's OK. But he takes Kyle Fletcher with him kind of spitefully

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/219a3057-3b87-40cf-95d6-da2d5e30b82a/20240703_183832.jpg)

HANGMAN ADAM PAGE HAS RETURNED AS THE ELITE SPONSORED WILD CARD!!!

*   ## **_OWEN HART CUP: HANGMAN ADAM PAGE DEF. JEFF JARRETT_**
    

Jarrett puts up as good a fight as he can but Hangman beats him senseless. Jarrett reverses a Buckshot into a Sharpshooter in honor of Owen Hart in a great moment. But it’s over shortly after.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ee7da2e4-5f5a-4e6a-bf0b-5a439ff2a66f/20240703_184211.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4abd29f1-d333-4b8b-8b4e-85380da2fc79/20240703_191210.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW INTERNATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP: WILL OSPREAY DEF. DANIEL GARCIA_**
    

MJF cost Garcia the match after distracting him with the prospect of using the Diamond Ring against Ospreay.

MJF then turns on Daniel Garcia. The Heel Scumbag has returned.

MJF beat Daniel Garcia for about 5 minutes straight before Garcia was stretchered out of the arena